'''古尔省'''（{{lang-fa|د غور ولايت}}）是[[阿富汗行政區劃|阿富汗34個省份]]之一，位於[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]中部偏西北的{{link-en|哈拉扎賈特|Hazarajat}}地區。古爾省設有10個[[縣_(阿富汗)|縣]]和數百個村落，人口約為657,200人<ref name=cso>{{cite web |url=http://cso.gov.af/Content/files/Ghor(1).pdf |title=Settled Population of Ghor province by Civil Division, Urban, Rural and Sex-2012-13 |publisher=Islamic Republic of Afghanistan: Central Statistics Organization |accessdate=2013-01-05 |archive-date=2014-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106040420/http://cso.gov.af/Content/files/Ghor(1).pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。省會是[[恰赫恰蘭|恰赫恰蘭]]。

